Subject: Data Classification config
Description:
Hello,

We are implementing a new on premise Endpoint Protector and would like to know if there is any individual configuration required for use with the Netwrix Data Classification system.
Solution_Comment__c:
We have informed the customer about our current support for metadata scanning, as the integration with NDC has yet to be tested.
The customer confirmed that they had a support meeting with NDC and they clarified the situation.
